# Tailwind (marketing)

## Mobile first

- Base styles for mobile; `md:` / `lg:` for larger breakpoints.

## Tokens

- Use semantic brand tokens from `src/app/globals.css` (`brand-cream`, `brand-turquoise`, etc.).
- Typography scales: `@/lib/typography` in TSX; `@utility` definitions in `globals.css`.
- Do not add one-off hex colors when a token exists.

## Spacing

- Section spacing via `MarketingSection` / component-system contract — avoid arbitrary `py-[NNpx]` on pages.
- Prefer Tailwind scale steps (`4`, `6`, `8`, `12`, `16`, `24`) for gaps and padding inside components.

## Alignment with app

- Token changes may need mirroring in `onetap-app` — note in PR.
